      <title>代码格式化配置</title>
      <link href="/archives/dc8644ca.html"/>
      <url>/archives/dc8644ca.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="开发工具-vsCode-之代码风格配置"><a href="#开发工具-vsCode-之代码风格配置" class="headerlink" title="开发工具 vsCode 之代码风格配置"></a>开发工具 vsCode 之代码风格配置</h1><h2 id="下载-vsCode"><a href="#下载-vsCode" class="headerlink" title="下载 vsCode"></a><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/Download">下载 vsCode</a></h2><h2 id="EditorConfig"><a href="#EditorConfig" class="headerlink" title="EditorConfig"></a>EditorConfig</h2><h3 id="Docs"><a href="#Docs" class="headerlink" title="Docs"></a><a href="https://editorconfig.org/">Docs</a></h3><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p>在vscode plugin market 中搜索 editorConfig 进行安装</p><img src="/archives/dc8644ca/installEditorConfig.png" class=""><h3 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h3><p>进入项目root目录下手动创建 .editorconfig 文件(右键鼠标，点击 Generate .editorconfig 选项, 可自动创建该配置文件), 并根据需求配置以下选项。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># EditorConfig is awesome: https://EditorConfig.org</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># top-most EditorConfig file</span><br><span class="line">root = true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 指定对该配置生效的文件</span><br><span class="line">[*.&#123;js,jsx,ts,tsx,vue,md&#125;]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 缩进风格 space / tab</span><br><span class="line">indent_style = space</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 缩进的大小</span><br><span class="line">indent_size = 2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 换行符 lf / cr / crlf</span><br><span class="line">end_of_line = lf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 字符编码格式</span><br><span class="line">charset = utf-8</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 是否删除每行末尾的空格</span><br><span class="line">trim_trailing_whitespace = false</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 是否文件最后一行插入换行符，并换行到下一行</span><br><span class="line">insert_final_newline = false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Prettier"><a href="#Prettier" class="headerlink" title="Prettier"></a>Prettier</h2><h3 id="Docs-1"><a href="#Docs-1" class="headerlink" title="Docs"></a><a href="https://prettier.io/docs/en/index.html">Docs</a></h3><h3 id="安装-1"><a href="#安装-1" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p>在vscode plugin market 中搜索 prettier 进行安装</p><img src="/archives/dc8644ca/installPrettier.png" class=""><h3 id="配置-1"><a href="#配置-1" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h3><p>在项目根目录下创建 .prettierrc 文件，添加配置项，参考如下</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;https://prettier.io/docs&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#1&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否使用制表符缩进, 默认值: false(空格缩进)&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;useTabs&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#2&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;缩进的空格数, 默认值: 2&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;tabWidth&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">2</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#3&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否在语句的末尾使用分号, 默认值: true&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;semi&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#4&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否使用单引号, 默认值: false(双引号)&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;singleQuote&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#5&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;每行语句的最大字符长度, 超出后自动换行, 默认值: 80&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;printWidth&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">100</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#6&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;在JSX中是否使用单引号, 默认值: false(双引号)&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;jsxSingleQuote&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#7&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;多行逗号分隔的语句结构中是否添加尾随逗号, 默认值: es5(对象, 数组). none 表示不添加, all 表示尽可能在后面添加逗号（包括函数参数）&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;trailingComma&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;none&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#8&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否使用引号包裹, 默认值: as-needed&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;quoteProps&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;as-needed&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#9&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;单个参数的箭头函数是否添加括号, 默认值: always(添加括号). avoid 表示尽可能的省略括号&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;arrowParens&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;always&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#10&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;换行格式, 默认值: lf. lf 表示仅换行(\n) 用于 Macos, Linux, cr 表示仅回车(\r) 不常用, crlf 表示回车+换行(\r\n) 用于 Windows&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;endOfLine&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;lf&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#11&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;花括号内的两边是否添加空格, 默认值: true&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;bracketSpacing&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#12&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;代码格式化的开始位置, 默认值: 0(文件开头)&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;rangeStart&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">0</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#13&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;代码格式化的结束位置, 默认值: null(文件结尾)&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;rangeEnd&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">null</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#14&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否换行, 默认值: preserve. always 表示超出设置的单行最大字符长度后自动换行, never 表示不换行&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;proseWrap&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;preserve&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#16&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否只格式化包含 @format 、 @prettier 头的文件, 默认值: false&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;requirePragma&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#17&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否在文件开头自动插入 @format 注释, 默认值: false&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;insertPragma&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#18&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否将包含多行JSX代码标签的 &gt; 符号放在最后一行的末尾(适用于非自闭合元素), 默认值: false&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;jsxBracketSameLine&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#19&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否缩进Vue文件中的脚本,样式和标签, 默认值: false&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;vueIndentScriptAndStyle&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#20&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;HTML文件中空白的敏感度, 默认值: css&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;htmlWhitespaceSensitivity&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;css&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;#21&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;是否自动识别代码文件, 默认值: auto&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;embeddedLanguageFormatting&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;auto&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="保存后自动格式代码"><a href="#保存后自动格式代码" class="headerlink" title="保存后自动格式代码"></a>保存后自动格式代码</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">打开 vscode 的设置(command键 + ,), 搜索 &quot;editor:format&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">将 Default Formatter 设置为 &quot;Prettier - Code Formatter&quot; 并将选项 &quot;Format On Save&quot; 选中。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/archives/dc8644ca/formatOnSave.png" class=""><h3 id="忽略文件"><a href="#忽略文件" class="headerlink" title="忽略文件"></a>忽略文件</h3><h4 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/archives/9b9637ae.html" title=".gitignore 文件编写规则">.gitignore 文件编写规则</a></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在 root 目录下创建 .prettierignore 指定忽略规则（规则与 gitignore 一致）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Nodejs-项目中使用"><a href="#Nodejs-项目中使用" class="headerlink" title="Nodejs 项目中使用"></a>Nodejs 项目中使用</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">安装 prettier 工具包</span><br><span class="line">npm i prettier -D 或</span><br><span class="line">yarn add prettier -D</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">在项目根目录下的 package.json 文件中添加脚本命令 &quot;prettier&quot;: &quot;prettier --write pathname&quot;。</span><br><span class="line">执行命令 npm run prettier 或 yarn prettier 对指定 pathname 下的文件或目录进行代码格式化。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="ESLint"><a href="#ESLint" class="headerlink" title="ESLint"></a>ESLint</h3>]]></content>
      
      
